explicitMods: ['20% increased Effect of your Marks', '14% Global chance to Blind Enemies on hit', 'Removes Bleeding when you use a Flask', "Hits ignore Enemy Monster Physical Damage Reduction if you've Blocked in the past 20 seconds"]
flavourText: ['Faith given under false pretenses still carries the same power.']

name: Watcher's Eye
